style=\"color: #88C0D0\">translation<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">bengali<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    <\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">ar<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        <\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">translation<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">arabic<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">i18n<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.<\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">use<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">(<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">initReactI18next<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">) <\/span><span style=\"color: #616E88\">\/\/ passes i18n down to react-i18next<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.<\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">init<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">(<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        <\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">resources<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        <\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">lng<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;<\/span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">en<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        <\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">fallbackLng<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;<\/span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">en<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        <\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">interpolation<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">            <\/span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">escapeValue<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">false<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    <\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">)<\/span><\/span><\/code><\/pre><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group doc-tip\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p><strong>TIP<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Recommended tutorial is below \ud83d\udc47<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"How to Change Language in StackFood\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/-gSOyS4ynQo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"change-app-color\"><strong>Change App color<a href=\"https:\/\/docs.6amtech.com\/docs-stack-food\/react-web-app\/customization#change-app-color\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u200b<\/a><\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To change the app color, follow the steps below-<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Open&nbsp;<kbd>&lt;project&gt;\/src\/theme\/light-theme-options.js<\/kbd>&nbsp;file and set preferred primary colors for light themes.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>In the same way open&nbsp;<kbd>&lt;project&gt;\/src\/theme\/dark-theme-options.js<\/kbd>&nbsp;file and set preferred primary, accent and etc. colors for dark theme.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group doc-tip\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p><strong>TIP<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Recommended tutorial is below \ud83d\udc47<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"How to Setup Theme and Color in StackFood React\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/jwVw8HH1QRY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"change-app-font\"><strong>Change App Font<a href=\"https:\/\/docs.6amtech.com\/docs-stack-food\/react-web-app\/customization#change-app-font\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u200b<\/a><\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To change website font you have to go to&nbsp;<kbd>&lt;project&gt;src\/theme\/base-theme-options<\/kbd>.then line 299 fontFamily: &#8216;<strong>&#8220;Signika Negative&#8221;<\/strong>,&nbsp;<strong>&#8220;sans-serif&#8221;<\/strong>&#8216;, replace fontFamily. Path:&nbsp;<kbd>project\/src\/theme\/base-theme-options<\/kbd>&nbsp;Example :&nbsp;<kbd>fontFamily:\u201dyour font family\u201d<\/kbd><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Country Filter\u200b To change the country filter, follow the steps below- TIP Recommended tutorial is below \ud83d\udc47 Add New Local Language\u200b To add a new language, follow the steps below- \/src\/language?\/i18n.js TIP Recommended tutorial is below \ud83d\udc47 Change App color\u200b To change the app color, follow the steps below- TIP Recommended tutorial is below \ud83d\udc47 &#8230; <a title=\"Customization Setup\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/stackfood.app\/documentation\/react-web-app\/customization-setup\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about Customization Setup\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"doc_category":[42],"doc_tag":[],"class_list":["post-21007","docs","type-docs","status-publish","hentry","doc_category-react-web-app"],"year_month":"2025-11","word_count":520,"total_views":0,"reactions":{"happy":0,"normal":0,"sad":0},"author_info":{"name":"sultan@6amtech.com","author_nicename":"sultan6amtech-com","author_url":"https:\/\/stackfood.app\/author\/sultan6amtech-com\/"},"doc_category_info":[{"term_name":"React Web App","term_url":"https:\/\/stackfood.app\/docs-category\/react-web-app\/"}],"doc_tag_info":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/stackfood.app\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs\/21007","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/stackfood.app\/wp-json\/wp\/